{
  "analysis": "I've implemented the common functions. Now I need to create the serial implementation. This will be the baseline implementation that other versions will be compared against.",
  "plan": "I'll implement the serial version in serial.c. This will include the main function, command-line argument parsing, simulation loop, and output handling according to the requirements.",
  "commands": [
